name: Kari Sweets
description:
Kari Sweets

If you were lucky like me to be a teenager in the nascent years of the internets, you'll remember the crazy popularity of "teen internet models."

These models sold pic sets behind a paywall that slowly graduated from bra-and-panties pics to softcore nudity. My favorite of them all was Kari Sweets and she's probably responsible for many of my preferences that have lasted into adulthood.

For reals, this is my favorite of all time.

Use a strength of 0.5-0.8.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

NOTE: This LoRA performs WAY better when you use consistentFactor_v30 for the model.
